PrecisSCHEDULE No. 867 to the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS - which establishes maximum residue limits (MRLs) on the amount of the miticide "CLOFENTEZINE" that can be detected in a number of foods, it being a miticide effective in the control of mites in the egg and immature stages.

precis:
SCHEDULE No. 867 to the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS - which establishes
maximum residue limits (MRLs) on the amount of the miticide "CLOFENTEZINE"
that can be detected in a number of foods, it being a miticide effective
in the control of mites in the egg and immature stages.
